WEBVTT

00:02.961 --> 00:04.296
I feel completely distraught.

00:04.338 --> 00:06.047
I didn't think we'd
go through with it.

00:06.089 --> 00:07.549
Now it's a lot of uncertainty.

00:07.591 --> 00:08.926
It's a shock.

00:08.968 --> 00:10.761
We're all in deep shit.

00:10.803 --> 00:12.930
Better the devil you
know, than you don't.

00:12.972 --> 00:14.139
It goes on.

00:14.181 --> 00:16.265
I feel it's like the
end of the world.

00:16.308 --> 00:17.518
It feels pretty bad.

00:17.559 --> 00:19.060
It's the ramifications
of it all.

00:19.102 --> 00:20.729
There doesn't seem
to be a plan for

00:20.771 --> 00:22.982
what we're going to do now.

00:23.022 --> 00:26.694
You don't know what to do,
because they're all arguing.

00:26.735 --> 00:31.762
It little woken them, but...
I think human beings

00:31.763 --> 00:36.036
are still stupid and
ego gets in the way.

00:37.329 --> 00:40.374
♪ I took a walk through this ♪

00:40.415 --> 00:43.377
♪ Beautiful world ♪

00:43.418 --> 00:45.295
♪ Felt the cool rain ♪

00:45.337 --> 00:48.007
♪ On my shoulder ♪

00:49.048 --> 00:51.092
♪ Found something good ♪

00:51.134 --> 00:54.972
♪ In this beautiful world ♪

00:55.014 --> 00:56.974
♪ I felt the rain ♪

