39:19.482 --> 39:21.483
I was feeling shame, and
regret, -and mourning...

39:21.484 --> 39:23.278
Yeah, you're not the only one.

39:23.320 --> 39:24.654
Don't know what's happening.

39:24.696 --> 39:27.073
Okay, I'm gonna give you
some eggs in Purgatory.

39:27.115 --> 39:28.407
Why Purgatory?

39:28.449 --> 39:31.203
Because they're in chili
sauce and tomatoes,

39:31.244 --> 39:32.411
special hangover cure.

39:32.453 --> 39:33.288
