you can just get the fats

40:29.073 --> 40:30.469
going into your mouth.

40:30.511 --> 40:31.679
Hmm.

40:31.721 --> 40:34.182
There is light and hope
in the universe again.

40:34.224 --> 40:35.878
- Thank you.
