40:35.892 --> 40:40.438
Spice, runny eggs, and
grease, just what I needed.

40:41.689 --> 40:43.086
Hmm, so good.

40:43.087 --> 40:44.483
I have something absolvent.

40:44.525 --> 40:46.861
You know that thing in "The
Simpsons" once when he wants

40:46.862 --> 40:49.072
to put on weight so he
doesn't have to go to work?

40:49.114 --> 40:51.908
And he allows himself to eat
things that when you rub it

40:50.531 --> 40:53.201
on something it makes it
go see-through, like that.

40:53.243 --> 40:54.493
"Your window to weight gain."

