about six months.

41:02.252 --> 41:03.962
I do feel quite pleased
that we can be

41:04.003 --> 41:05.297
a corrupting influence.

41:05.338 --> 41:07.132
That's something that
we can be proud of.

41:10.551 --> 41:13.512
These are frightening
times for many.

41:13.554 --> 41:15.724
The world is changing,
and there is no stopping

41:15.725 --> 41:16.808
those changes.

41:16.849 --> 41:20.812
But in such times, there
are always two ways to go,

41:20.853 --> 41:25.358
run and hide, build walls,
cower in fear and suspicion,

41:25.400 --> 41:28.674
point the finger at our
neighbors, look, like desperate,

41:28.675 --> 41:32.031
frightened people do,
for someone to blame,

41:32.073 --> 41:35.910
or stand up and try... at least
try to build a better world,

41:35.952 --> 41:39.205
to look for, instead of a
man on a horse to save us

41:39.247 --> 41:43.501
or a wall to keep us apart,
to our better angels.

